description: Fleetwood Town come from behind to beat Milton Keynes Dons 4-2 at Stadium MK.
title: Milton Keynes Dons 2-4 Fleetwood Town
title_page: Milton Keynes Dons 2-4 Fleetwood Town - BBC Sport
maintext:
MK Dons have failed to win any of their last six league games against Fleetwood Town (D3 L3), losing each of their last three in succession.
After winning their last away league game against MK Dons in December 2022, Fleetwood Town will be looking to take consecutive wins at Stadium MK for the first time.
MK Dons have won just two of their last nine home league games (D2 L5), though one did come in their last outing during a 2-1 victory over Morecambe.
